## RULE 03 — H.264 COPY Path: Always Add Bitstream Filter (LL-006)

Whenever writing -c:v copy for H.264 content destined for MPEG-TS, ALWAYS add
h264_mp4toannexb. No exceptions.

    from exstreamtv.ffmpeg.constants import BSF_H264_ANNEXB

    if video_format == VideoFormat.COPY:
        cmd.extend(["-c:v", "copy"])
        cmd.extend(["-bsf:v", BSF_H264_ANNEXB])  # REQUIRED — not optional

Without this, the first GOP is corrupted or black on all decoders.

